Class DecimalQuaternion

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.util.group.Quad<BigDecimal>

civitas.celestis.math.vector.DecimalQuaternion
All Implemented Interfaces:
BigVector<BigDecimal,Decimal4>, DecimalVector<Decimal4>, Vector<BigDecimal,Decimal4>, Collectable<BigDecimal>, Listable<BigDecimal>, Group<BigDecimal>, Groupable<BigDecimal>, Tuple<BigDecimal>, Transformable<BigDecimal>, Serializable, Iterable<BigDecimal>
public class DecimalQuaternion extends Decimal4
A quaternion is used to represent the rotation of a three-dimensional vector.
